balladur maintain 1987 french inflat target financ minist edouard balladur said he wa maintain hi 2.5 pct inflat target for 1987 after the announc earlier today of a 3.4 pct year-on-year rise in retail price for februari . he told a radio interview he saw no reason to revi hi target for 1987 after the februari monthli result of between 0.1 to o.2 pct , follow a 0.9 pct rise in januari ( three pct year on year ) that forc the govern to revi an earlier target of two pct to a current 2.5 pct . he said he wa happi with `` a good result `` for februari but stress a need for continu `` vigil `` against inflat . a financ ministri statement said the year-on-year differenti between french and lower west german inflat rate , calcul on the last three month , had narrow in februari to two to 2.3 pct compar to 2.7 pct in januari . if calcul on the last 12 month , the differenti came to 3.9 pct , the statement said , ad `` the tendenc is therefor one of a lessen of the inflat gap with our main trade partner . ``